ing dog’.","English:"]},{"name":"Rotchford","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Irish Caitlin.","Irish and English: variant of   Rochford  ."]}]},{"name":"Ralph","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["From a Norman French name, <i>Raulf</i>, a contracted form of the Germanic personal name <i>Radulf</i>, derived from <i>rād</i> ‘counsel’ + <i>wulf</i> ‘wolf’. The spelling with <i>-ph</i> is due to classical influence in the 18th century."],"variants":[{"name":"Ralf","meanings":["From a Norman French name, <i>Raulf</i>, a contracted form of the Germanic personal name <i>Radulf</i>, derived from <i>rād</i> ‘counsel’ + <i>wulf</i> ‘wolf’. The spelling with <i>-ph</i> is due to classical influence in the 18th century."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Ralph I Rochford was born in 1220, in Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Joan le Breton. He died in 1285, at the age of 65."},"et":{"1220–1285":"1220–1285","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","1225":"1225","1220":"1220","1285":"1285","1250":"1250","Fenn in Boston, Lincolnshire, England":"Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1220–1285":"1220–1285","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","1225":"1225","1220":"1220","1285":"1285","1250":"1250","Fenn in Boston, Lincolnshire, England":"Lincolnshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1220–1285":"1220–1285","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","1225":"1225","1220":"1220","1285":"1285","1250":"1250","Fenn in Boston, Lincolnshire, England":"Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Ralph I Rochford est né en 1220, à Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Joan le Breton. Il est décédé en 1285, à l’âge de 65 ans."},"de":{"1220–1285":"1220–1285","1225–Female":"1225–Verstorben","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","1225":"1225","1220":"1220","1285":"1285","1250":"1250","Fe